%section#gangster.gangster.dd-container
      
  %h2.gangster-title 
    "Ever since I was a kid, I always wanted to be a gangster."
      
  =image_tag 'home/gangster.svg'

  %p.instead
    But instead, I'm a front-end developer...

%section#datacamp.dd-container
  
  =image_tag 'home/datacamp-logo.svg', class: 'dd-db dd-mhc datacamp-logo', width: '340'
  
  .datacamp
    
    .dd-card.datacamp-card

      %p
        As the lead Front-end Developer at <a class="dd-link datacamp-link" href="https://www.datacamp.com">DataCamp</a>, I'm currently working with awesome people to implement a design system across multiple apps with various tech stacks.

      %p
        If you would enjoy building educational products with an awesome group of people, we're <a class="dd-link datacamp-link" href="https://www.datacamp.com/careers">hiring!</a>

    .datacamp-screenshot

      =image_tag 'home/screenshot-datacamp.jpg'


%section#frontendconf.dd-container.frontendconf

  %h2.dd-h2.frontendconf-title
    We used to run a conference...
  
  =image_tag 'home/dan-cherrie-stage.svg'

  %p.dd-measure-660
    My wife, Cherrie, and I co-founded the <a class="dd-link" href="http://frontenddesignconference.com">Front-End Design Conference</a> in St. Pete, Florida, in 2009 and ran it through 2015. These days we're glorified attendees, but it's still going! 

%section#projects.projects

  .projects-content
  
    .dd-container

      %h2.dd-h2 A few of my favorite personal projects

      .dd-trio
        
        .dd-trio-item
          .raisercise.dd-u-fx-fg1.dd-pa-40

            = image_tag 'http://placehold.it/800x600'
            
            %h3.dd-h3.dd-mt-20.dd-tac 
              Raisercise
            
            %p
              I learned how to build a small PWA with Preact and Firebase, in order to make an app that could tell me when to increase weights at the gym.

        .dd-trio-item
          .track-life.dd-u-fx-fg1.dd-pa-40

            = image_tag 'http://placehold.it/800x600'

            %h3.dd-h3.dd-mt-20.dd-tac 
              Track Life

            %p
              I love music, I dig data, and I wanted to make an app with vanilla JavaScript. This show's track peformance of the top 10 in Spotify for a short range of time.

        .dd-trio-item
          .roulettingale.dd-u-fx-fg1.dd-pa-40

            = image_tag 'http://placehold.it/800x600'
            
            %h3.dd-h3.dd-mt-20.dd-tac Roulettingale

            %p
              In addition to wanting being a gangster, I've been fascinated by gambling systems since I was young. This is a (non-responsive) log of testing one in Roulette.